<h1 id="Introduction"><a href="#Introduction" class="headerlink" title="Introduction"></a>Introduction</h1><p>This is a sample page for showcasing diffirent functions of hexo posting.<br>這是一個示範頁面，用來展示 Hexo Post 的不同功能。<br>You may link yourself to diffirent functions by the left sidebar.<br>您可以從左側的側邊欄連結到不同的區域。</p>
<p>Reference &#x2F; 參考 :<br><a href="https://zenreal.github.io/posts/44730/#">https://zenreal.github.io/posts/44730/#</a><br><a href="https://guanqr.com/tech/website/hexo-theme-next-customization/">https://guanqr.com/tech/website/hexo-theme-next-customization/</a></p>
