</div>
<p>This page is hidden until you click the ‘ Read More ‘ button.<br>在您按下「閱讀全文」內容按鈕前，此頁面已被隱藏。</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h1 id="Introduction"><a href="#Introduction" class="headerlink" title="Introduction"></a>Introduction</h1><p>基於 Victor-Cloux (V大) 預科作业3.0<br>電繪中，線條和色彩臨摹 的訓練。<br>這是一個 線條和色彩臨摹 的訓練圖生成器。</p>
<p>Based on Victor-Cloux (V大) Matriculation 3.0<br>Line and Color Imitation Training in Digital Art.<br>This is a Line and Color Imitation Training Images Generator.</p>
<h1 id="How-to-use"><a href="#How-to-use" class="headerlink" title="How to use?"></a>How to use?</h1><ol>
<li>Download the zip file from the link.<br>從連結下載壓縮檔。</li>
<li>Unzip the zip file.<br>解壓縮。</li>
<li>Open the Art_Practice_Generate Folder.<br>開啟 Art_Practice_Generate 資料夾。</li>
<li>Double click to run each .exe according to the order from 1 to 4.<br>按照 1 到 4 的順序，雙擊執行每個 .exe。</li>
<li>For 4_Color.exe , You can change colors by Right Clicking the screen. 對於 4_Color.exe ,<br>您可以用滑鼠右鍵按下螢幕來改變顏色。</li>
<li>Save the image by clicking the right top button.<br>按一下右上方的按鈕，儲存影像。</li>
<li>You will get 1 Line Practice &amp; 1 Color Practice with Date !<br>您將獲得 1 份線條練習和 1 份色彩練習，附有日期！</li>
</ol>
